in consideration of its auto industry's size, Ford's existing
investment here and the country's central location within ASEAN.
</P>
<P>
The new headquarters would take overall charge of all Ford's
strategic operations in the region and oversee plans to establish
a presence in Indonesia, according to Snyder. 
