was terribly overloaded. The vehicle was carrying about 70
passengers.
</P>
<P>
Abas Ronda, one of the survivors whose was injured, said the
truck veered and turned upside down until it fell into the ravine.
</P>
<P>
Ten injured passengers were declared in critical condition at a
local hospital. 
