<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, August 9 (Xinhua) -- Wang Liping, chairman of the
Shanghai Municipal Committee of the Chinese People's Political
Consultative Conference (CPPCC), met here today with a visiting
delegation of Taiwan's Alliance for the Reunification of China.
</P>
<P>
