the stance of the Taiwan authorities headed by Lee Teng-hui, but
by no means the will of the Taiwan people.
</P>
<P>
The delegation members said that they will firmly stick to
China's territorial integrity and the "one China" principle, and
will exchange views with people of all walks of people on the
mainland on the peaceful reunification of China, and express the
Taiwan compatriots' aspirations for peace and reunification.
